Matthew Schanche gives us an update on the Truth Matters podcast, upcoming in-person events, and current events relevant to Bible prophecy. 

Startling new developments show how close we are to the fulfillment of the no buy no sell prophecy. In our next Truth Matters podcast we’re going to talk about how the launch of FedNow is an important step toward no buy no sell. We’ll also discuss Elon Musk, his changes to Twitter, SpaceX, and his WEF connections. What’s all this got to do with Lucis Trust and the 2025 initiative? Join us on upcoming Truth Matters episodes as we discuss these topics.
